{"profile":{"awsPrograms":[{"category":"Serverless Hero","joinedAt":2022.0,"memberStatus":"ACTIVE","programName":"HERO"}],"basicInfo":{"alias":"allenheltondev","avatar":"https://avatars.builderprofile.aws.dev/32WXy3F6yVBpRwjTdu0TCJ0AEP2.webp","bio":"I’m an Ecosystem Engineer at Momento with a background in building scalable, event-driven systems. These days, I spend a lot of time exploring how AI agents can actually work at enterprise scale. I focus on challenges like determinism, orchestration, and fault tolerance.\n\nI enjoy sharing what I learn. I write, livestream, and host podcasts to help developers understand complex systems in a way that feels approachable and practical.\n\nCommunity is at the core of everything I do. From the Believe in Serverless community to conference talks and one-on-one mentoring, I try to make space where people can learn and build together. I believe good humans build good technology, and I do my best to live that out in everything I do.\n\nHappy coding!","builderProfileId":"cac0aa93-4fb1-4538-abfa-05c872c98442","createdOn":1.712091430912E12,"headline":"","isStaff":false,"name":"Allen Helton"},"location":{"displayLocation":{"countryRegion":"US","stateProvince":"TX"}},"profileStatus":"ACTIVE","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/allenheltondev","linkedIn":"https://linkedin.com/in/allenheltondev"}}}